{"tid":483754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點撚解食飯唔可以食甜野先？","createTime":"2017-11-29T12:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T12:40:02.000Z","uid":112643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"41436cb3452e3915109acf8e4179c495ec01291f","tid":483754,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"由細到大都俾人灌輸食野要食鹹野先，最好笑係老母話食甜再食鹹會生痔瘡。細細個去親食自助餐拎甜品先一定俾人屌，又話蠢又話唔抵食。大個咗拎甜品先又會俾fd笑，係同女朋友食會好少少。屌我心諗：我食一舊甜品都抵過你塊爛鬼豬牛雞排啦下話。真心一問，有無美食撚可以話我知，點撚解唔可以食甜野先？"},{"pid":"e77651f756bcb2449f879722ad16e6da9bab202f","tid":483754,"uid":77948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:18:26.000Z","msg":"因為會生痔瘡"},{"pid":"ce64bd5c4af532453fbc0b891dd4fa49e8b1cdcc","tid":483754,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為會生痔瘡</blockquote><br />\n咁你一定成日生痔瘡"},{"pid":"90cdd89977a14aa537ccfde66e67587e9c4b5fd6","tid":483754,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"先苦後甜"},{"pid":"504541263bce74a240f0318e97739bd0388bdb2d","tid":483754,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"因為你個胃壁掂到甜品嘅糖分之後就會產生糖反射，咁你個胃就會停止／緩慢蠕動，咁你咪冇乜胃口因為食欲下降左。"},{"pid":"a7ae2a1cea1b58d1484ec2eaaf3643ff99ec3465","tid":483754,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先苦後甜</blockquote><br />\n你餐餐食苦瓜飲廿四味？"},{"pid":"d1d1de32434e9fac31e832b0d4775a54ad2aac94","tid":483754,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你個胃壁掂到甜品嘅糖分之後就會產生糖反射，咁你個胃就會停止／緩慢蠕動，咁你咪冇乜胃口因為食欲下降左。</blockquote><br />\n但係我食肉仲快飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04de34084f1079e72d0f0da8df424f9dee3e644","tid":483754,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote